The Wall street journal data scrapper.

This is a scrapy project, before cloning it you should install some dependences.

	>sudo apt-get install python-dev python-pip libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev libffi-dev libssl-dev
	> sudo pip install xlrd xlutils

You can change destination folder for xls files in xlssettings.py

To start crawling type:

	> scrapy crawl wsjspider

The scraper saves data in xls format, but you can export it in any scrapy output files.

